title: Rada I Co Cafe-bistro
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, International, Western, Buffet, Fast food
description: A branch of the cafe network run by Krishnas, upstairs at Gaura Culture Centre, which includes a temple and a vegetarian food store. Simple design, a range of vegetarian meals including soups, stews, pies and sweets, as well as tea and herbal infusions. Some vegan options. No alcohol.
